# AviationWX Cron Jobs
# Runs inside Docker container
# Format: minute hour day month weekday user command

# Webcam refresh - every minute
* * * * * www-data cd /var/www/html && /usr/local/bin/php fetch-webcam-safe.php > /dev/null 2>&1

# Weather refresh - every minute
* * * * * www-data cd /var/www/html && /usr/local/bin/php fetch-weather-safe.php > /dev/null 2>&1

